{
  "stem": "304.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had holes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the holes had to match perfectly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Otherwise, they had to take it back to another department to chisel it off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it take ten times more times to take off one-- 20 times more than to make one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the girls worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we made, like, 500 pieces a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then they pushed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they make 800.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they brought it up to a thousand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when the SS saw-- and the foremens were older German civilians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when they saw that we can make a thousand-- and one day, they announced if you make 1,500 a day, you will get a bonus.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A bonus, some extra food, was very, very tempting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "By that time-- this was quite-- after several weeks that we were-- we were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And this was-- already I learned to do some sabotage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were two ways.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One way was when I did welding the-- when I was welding, I moved a little bit the part, the little metal part, so they didn't cover completely the holes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then it had to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I will-- with this, I could slow down the, the process.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I felt it's-- now, I was very careful that no-- if the foreman was there or SS, then I didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the other thing was I got-- I organized myself a piece of chalk because the people-- the men who brought the pipes and the pieces to the machine, every time they brought a batch, they made a chalk mark.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And every chalk mark meant how many pieces we made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then I organized those-- the, the chalk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "When we had already several lines-- even my partner didn't know it-- I always added an extra line.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
